<div id="folder" class="theme keep-you-figure-before-2012" style="background:url(../../../var/london/storage/images/formules/journees-a-theme/gardez-la-ligne-avant-2012/640-2-fre-FR/Gardez-la-ligne-avant-2012.jpg) no-repeat;">
            <div class="description">
            
<p class=" text-justify">The Olympic Games are approaching and it’s time to coach yourself if you want to give of your best&nbsp;! Discover different area of London through a green and sporty day. On your marks, get set, go…</p>

<ul>

<li>Combine a sightseeing tour with a regular workout&nbsp; with a 7km jogging on the riverside </li>

<li>Lunch looking out onto the Olympic &amp; Paralympic Park</li>

<li>Discover the Olympic Games venues by bike with a private guide and keep your bike for the rest of the day</li>

<li>Swim in the only Olympic size outdoor swimming pool&nbsp;! </li>

<li>Coffee break well-deserved in a nice little street</li>

</ul>
<p>Adult : from £97</p>
<p class=" text-justify">Don’t hesitate to <a href="../../Contact" target="_self">contact us</a>
&nbsp;if you need more information from now.</p>
<p class="notice">The price is calculated on a base of a group of 4 persons and includes activities, transport, refreshments, organisation of your day, a full programme to guide you. This programme is not contractual; it can change depending on the season, the weather and our providers. Therefore, a quotation of the above trip will be issued upon request.</p>

